_sText: This is an aim map designed to be headshot only. Use it to practice against bots (videos: http://tinyurl.com/y9d57gd http://tinyurl.com/ya28mg5 ) or with your friends or in a random pub. You cannot rush the tunnels are too long you would die, but you can get to the other spawn to kill afks/campers You spawn with an AK, deagle, vesthelm for the fairness, but you can also buy whatever you want. Bots run a course kind of like a tower defense so it's really good to use this to practice against bots. Please click here for more information http://y3sak.crazedhosting.com/wb/pages/aim_tex_headshot-tower-d-explanation.php it's my website. Has a lot more info on the map and an alternative download link.
